inputs.text: 1boy, solo, she tied her long hair into two playful ponytails, her middle hair was trimmed neatly, and her long bangs slightly covered her forehead, revealing a pair of smart blue eyes. She was wearing a light purple short-sleeved top with round neck, with ruffles at the cuffs, a pair of high-waisted white shorts on her lower body, and a pair of white sneakers on her feet. The overall look was full of youthfulness.

inputs.show_text: 1boy，Solo，她将长发绑成两只嬉戏的马尾辫，中间的头发整齐地修剪了，长长的刘海略微遮住了额头，露出了一双聪明的蓝色眼睛。她穿着浅紫色的短袖顶，上面有圆脖子，袖口上有荷叶边，她的下半身上的一双高腰白色短裤，脚上的一双白色运动鞋。总体外观充满了年轻。
